      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under the <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool</p><p>Once cool, squeeze the water out of the spinach as much as you can then chop it roughly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-11-19_10h33m09s-APIC-1582646223312-x200.jpg",
