            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach </strong>and<strong> smoked mackerel pieces </strong>to the pan with the <strong>drained tortiglioni</strong> and a big splash of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong>,<strong> </strong>then cook for 1-2 min until the fish is warmed through</p><p>Add your<strong> crème fraîche </strong>and<strong> </strong>the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>to the pan with your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/28-11-19_10h37m24s-APIC-1582646228608-x200.jpg",
