          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined and the sauce begins to stick to the tortiglioni – this is your <strong>creamy smoked mackerel tortiglioni with chilli & lemon</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
